==English==
===Etymology===
From [[tele-]] + [[commute]]

===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb|telecommut|ing}}

#{{cattag|Computing}} To [[work]] from [[home]], sometimes for part of a working day or week, using a [[computer]] connected to one's [[employer]]'s [[network]] or via the [[Internet]]

